    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a rewarding hands-on project? This vehicle is looking for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little elbow grease! While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly way to build their dream ride. It's an honest car with lots of potential for the right person to bring back to life!",
