    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the wheel arches, several large dents, and faded paint across the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin requires a deep clean, as the upholstery is torn and several plastic trim pieces are missing or broken. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable knock and a persistent oil leak, and the brakes will need replacement very soon. This car is best suited for someone looking for a major project or for those in need of spare parts.",
