      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, currently held in showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard, exhibiting flawless coachwork and a pristine interior environment that retains its original luster. Every mechanical system has been vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the most discerning enthusiast who prioritizes uncompromising quality and automotive integrity.",
